            "text": "while ignoring the relationship between arguments . <S>",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "This paper proposes a Regularization-Based Pattern Balancing Method ( RBPB ) . <S>",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 12,
            "text": "Inspired by the progress in representation learning , ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
